import React from 'react'; import './DailyScorePopup.scss'; const DailyScorePopup = ({ dailyData }) => { if (!dailyData) return null; // If no data, don't render return (

Daily Driving Summary

Driving Score

{dailyData.driving_score} / 100

Driving Category

{dailyData.driving_category}

Total Distance Covered

{dailyData.total_distance_covered_km} km

Average Speed

{dailyData.aggregated_data['Speed(km/h)']} km/h

Acceleration

{dailyData.aggregated_data['Acceleration(m/s^2)']} m/s²

Jerk

{dailyData.aggregated_data['Jerk(m/s^3)']} m/s³

Braking Intensity

{dailyData.aggregated_data['Braking_Intensity']}

Speed Violations

{dailyData.aggregated_data['Speed_Violation']}

SASV (Sudden Acceleration/Speed Violation)

{dailyData.aggregated_data['SASV']}

); }; export default DailyScorePopup;
